text: After dressing up as a Victoria's Secret costume and as pop star Ariana Grande on Wednesday, Kourtney Kardashian rounded out the Halloween trifecta with an obscure costume and several friends. Kardashian, 39, took to Instagram to showcase her third and final costume for Halloween, dressing up as'Fook Mi'( Diane Mizota ) from 2002's Austin Powers in Goldmember. She was joined by singer and Kendall Jenner's pal Fai Khadra dressed as Austin Powers ( Mike Myers ) and Stephanie Shepherd as Fook Yu ( Carrie Ann Inaba ).
